snippet.textDisplay: Was always a fan of Punjab and its culture, but now with the recent events came to know about the violence culture there too, broke my heart, which always saw Punjab as a place of peace filled fields. Marne wale aur badla lene wale dono hi na rahe to har taraf shanti hi shanti hogi. Hope the government do something about this and restore Punjab's old peaceful glory. This song somehow brings in a wind of calm into my mind, have been listening in a loop since I discovered it. Maan sahab da jawab nai.
